5.3 DUIM-Sheets Module

gesture-keysym

Generic function

Summary

Returns the keysym associated with the specified gesture.

Signature

gesture-keysym keyboard-gesture => keysym

Arguments

keyboard-gesture
An instance of type <keyboard-gesture>.

Values

keysym
An instance of type <symbol>.

Library

duim-sheets

Module

duim-sheets

Description

Returns the keysym associated with keyboard-gesture.

See also

<keyboard-gesture>, page 291
